{"tid":617990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂徹底完蛋了？ 【PC用】Switch模擬器已可運行遊戲軟件","createTime":"2018-04-05T12:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T08:04:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"319664d894d7ef4114f1bdbce442d8585398516d","tid":617990,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"2018/04/05 20:43<br />\n在今年1月份的時候，CEMU（任天堂WiiU模擬器）和Citra（任天堂3DS模擬器）背後的製作團隊曝光了其還在試驗中的任天堂Switch模擬器「yuzu」，不過這個模擬器還處於非常初始的階段，沒啥意義。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過好消息來啦！最近，國外技術大牛們又研制出了一款新的Switch模擬器「RyujiNX」，這款模擬器相比「yuzu」可謂進步巨大，現在它已經可以啓動一些Switch的遊戲了！我們為大家獻上了兩段「RyujiNX」啓動Switch遊戲的視頻，一起來看看吧！"},{"pid":"5cd01a9de6f705ddfc59ed5a4b2bf04b17148265","tid":617990,"uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"319664d894d7ef4114f1bdbce442d8585398516d","tid":617990,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"2018/04/05 20:43<br />\n在今年1月份的時候，CEMU（任天堂WiiU模擬器）和Citra（任天堂3DS模擬器）背後的製作團隊曝光了其還在試驗中的任天堂Switch模擬器「yuzu」，不過這個模擬器還處於非常初始的階段，沒啥意義。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過好消息來啦！最近，國外技術大牛們又研制出了一款新的Switch模擬器「RyujiNX」，這款模擬器相比「yuzu」可謂進步巨大，現在它已經可以啓動一些Switch的遊戲了！我們為大家獻上了兩段「RyujiNX」啓動Switch遊戲的視頻，一起來看看吧！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"視你老母頻<br />\n<br />\n同埋模擬器效能夠玩Switch games？"},{"pid":"fa346a767c86f4817565af13cc89be76baa7fb99","tid":617990,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e21bf740104d0cd38b4702abe235dd102f3f720","tid":617990,"uid":9231,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"買左機<br />\n但係冇野玩 擺左係度封塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fd26714be0215543f4a2f4b3c9ebf4dc665328","tid":617990,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://v.ali213.net/video/180405/252309.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.ali213.net%2Fvideo%2F180405%2F252309.html&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0a118acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://v.ali213.net/video/180405/252309.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSwitch模擬器「RyujiNX」啓動《洞窟物語》<br />\n<br />\n視頻地址：<a href=\"http://v.ali213.net/video/180405/252307.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.ali213.net%2Fvideo%2F180405%2F252307.html&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=02e132cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://v.ali213.net/video/180405/252307.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我們看到，「RyujiNX」目前已經可以進入Switch遊戲《噗喲噗喲俄羅斯方塊》和《洞窟物語》的啓動畫面了，這是人類的一小步，卻是Switch模擬器的一大步！根據相關描述，「RyujiNX」是一款用「C#」語言編程的Switch模擬器，目標是提供流暢優秀的Switch遊戲體驗，友好的用戶界面和可靠的穩定性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    很顯然，我們無法指望短期內用模擬器玩到任天堂Switch的3A大作，但是這款模擬器可以啓動遊戲，這看起來依然很酷。<br />\n<br />\n如果你對這款模擬器有興趣，可以點擊這裡下載，但製作團隊表示目前這款模擬器還很不穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRyujiNX模擬Switch  網站地址： <a href=\"https://zoltx23.github.io/ryujinx-emu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzoltx23.github.io%2Fryujinx-emu%2F&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c227d00a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zoltx23.github.io/ryujinx-emu/</a>"},{"pid":"81b6eb18d0bcd7f4abd87e95b389a09e3859aa29","tid":617990,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"成部desktop fing來fing去？<br />\n<br />\n點玩？"},{"pid":"402864b6d3b2ec74409e90696c5563f596db7c82","tid":617990,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"06fd26714be0215543f4a2f4b3c9ebf4dc665328","tid":617990,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://v.ali213.net/video/180405/252309.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.ali213.net%2Fvideo%2F180405%2F252309.html&d=9473INngZ